In <b>C</b>, we have 1 to 26 <b>elements</b> in the form of <b>matrix</b> of 5 rows and 5 columns.
<p>So <b>C</b> is a <b>two dimensional array.</b>
</p>

24
00:02:40 --> 00:02:44
